title: Money Tree 2: Cash Grow Game
description: Money Tree 2 is the ultimate game to become the world's wealthiest business tycoon! Live the life of a billionaire and use your idle money to build your own empire. Grow your wealth like trees and buy the most expensive cars, houses, yachts, and jewelry. Hire celebrities to help you manage your endless cash and invest in a range of luxury items. If you dream of being a billionaire, "Cash Tycoon" is the perfect clicker game for you!
